{"type": "post", "post": {"team": "marketing_team", "channel": "q2_budget_discussion", "user": "ethan.thompson", "message": "Thanks for the update, Sarah! It's great to see our marketing efforts aligning with our sustainability goals. If there are any specific campaigns that stood out this quarter, I'd love to hear about them.", "create_at": 1620500001000}}
{"type": "post", "post": {"team": "marketing_team", "channel": "q2_budget_discussion", "user": "sarah.james", "message": "Absolutely, Ethan! We focused heavily on digital campaigns and influencer partnerships, which I think will really resonate with our target audience. I'll share a detailed report on campaign performances next week.", "create_at": 1620500002000}}
